          "type": "unknown",
          "description": "User natural-language task description (passed verbatim from external taskDescription input). Renamed from \"description\" to disambiguate from analyzing.outputs.pipelineDescription — see dogfood Finding 7 (2026-04-25)."
        },
        {
          "name": "rejectionFeedback",
          "type": "string",
          "description": "User free-text correction supplied at the awaitingConfirm gate via answer_gate({answer:\"reject\", comment:<this>}). Empty string on the first pass before the gate has fired; populated on reject-rerun. The analyzing agent must read this and, when non-empty, adjust its design accordingly."
